5149 - Groceries and Related Products, Not Elsewhere Classified Summary > VOTORANTIM INTERNATIONAL AUSTRALIA PTY LTD (formerly A.C.N. 108 749 631 PTY LTD) is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover groceries and related products, not elsewhere classified. The company is involved in the import but not export of goods. VOTORANTIM INTERNATIONAL AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is headquartered in Sydney, New South Wales. It is headed by managing director Andrew Edward Kesik. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $33.20 million. Its net profit totalled $389,000. VOTORANTIM INTERNATIONAL AUSTRALIA PTY LTD forms part of the wholesale trade industry sector.
